def module spearswap
def desc "Swaps to spear, lunges, and swaps back in one key"

on key_press C if playing if_not blocking if hotbar_has #spear {
   wait 0.05
   switch #spear
   input left
   wait 0.07 switch back
}

Is it possible to:
1. switch to `#plank` if in hotbar (to have least cooldown)
2. then, spear, click, wait, switch BACK TO the original hotbar slot (not plank)